  h3 Tables
  p 
    | Tables come with helper styles for changing the default appearance. The default table markup can be found below &mdash; do remember about proper content grouping with 
    code.inline-light thead
    |  and 
    code.inline-light tbody
    | .

  pre
    code
      = '<table>'
      br
      = '  <thead>'
      br
      = '    <tr>'
      br
      = '     <th>#</th>'
      br
      = '     <th>Name</th>'
      br
      = '     <th>Surname</th>'
      br
      = '     <th>Email</th>'
      br
      = '    </tr>'
      br
      = '  </thead>'
      br
