  h4 Outlined table with hover effect
  p 
    | To separate the table visually add 
    code.inline-light table-outlined
    |  class. For additional hover effect on rows use 
    code.inline-light table-with-hover
    |  .

  table.table-outlined.table-with-hover
    thead
      tr
        th #
        th Name
        th Surname
        th Email
    tbody
      tr
        td 1
        td Adam
        td Brault
        td 
          a adam@andyet.net
      tr
        td 2
        td Henrik 
        td Joreteg
        td 
          a henrik@andyet.net
      tr
        td 3
        td Adam
        td Baldwin
        td
          a baldwin@andyet.net

  h4 Striped table
  p
    | To differentiate the rows add 
    code.inline-light table-striped
    |  class to the 
    code.inline-light table
    |  tag.

  table.table-striped
    thead
      tr
        th #
        th Name
        th Surname
        th Email
    tbody
      tr
        td 1
        td Adam
        td Brault
        td 
          a adam@andyet.net
      tr
        td 2
        td Henrik 
        td Joreteg
        td 
          a henrik@andyet.net
      tr
        td 3
